document_data.name: Fomoyn
document_data.mainbody: '''Fomoyn the Swift''' was a male [[wood elf]] [[rogue]] and [[ranger]] of the village of [[Reitheillaethor]] in the [[High Forest]].
document_data.Personality: Outspoken and xenophobic, Fomoyn the Swift had a reputation for his ability to hunt [[orc]]s.
